<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٨٢٥ - ش ط ن]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شطَنَ/ شطَنَ عن يشطُن، شُطُونًا، فهو شاطن، والمفعول مشطون عنه<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• شطَنتِ الدّارُ:</span> بَعُدَت.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• شطَن عنه:</span> بَعُدَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>